---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="YeahVibe Roadmap – HappyBein"
  description="Three-phase roadmap for YeahVibe: from foundation and community expansion to an AI-powered global decision-support ecosystem."
  canonical="https://happybein.com/roadmap"
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="section-label">The Evolution of YeahVibe</div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-ink tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-4 max-w-2xl"
          style="font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.9rem);">Refining the Instrument for a Complex World</h1>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl">YeahVibe is a living instrument designed to simplify complexity. Our roadmap is a commitment to building a decision-support ecosystem that empowers individuals and organisations to act with clarity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto">
      <div class="section-label">🛤 Where We Are Going</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-8" style="font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2.2rem);">Roadmap</h2>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 grid gap-6 items-start" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); border-left:4px solid #2ABFBF; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(26,153,154,0.12); grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-display font-black text-teal-dark text-[1.2rem]" style="background:#E8F7F7;">1</div>
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block text-2xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-2 py-1 rounded-full mb-2" style="background:rgba(42,191,191,0.12); color:#1A9A9A;">Active / Continuous Refinement</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink text-[1.15rem] mb-2">Phase 1: Foundation — The Instrument</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-3">Perfecting the core modular engine that helps you make better decisions.</p>
            <ul class="ml-4 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1">
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Refine the Core:</strong> Enhancing <a href="https://yeahvibe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-dark font-semibold">YeahVibe.com</a> as a user-friendly repository.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Library Expansion:</strong> Curating "Life Recipes" for real-world challenges.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Feedback Loop:</strong> Integrating user insights to solve actual problems.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 grid gap-6 items-start" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); border-left:4px solid #4CAF50; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(26,153,154,0.12); grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-display font-black text-teal-dark text-[1.2rem]" style="background:#E8F7F7;">2</div>
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block text-2xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-2 py-1 rounded-full mb-2" style="background:rgba(76,175,80,0.1); color:#388E3C;">In Progress</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink text-[1.15rem] mb-2">Phase 2: Expansion — The Community</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-3">Transitioning from a static tool to a dynamic, multilingual resource.</p>
            <ul class="ml-4 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1">
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Multilingual Frameworks:</strong> Breaking language barriers globally.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Interactive Tools:</strong> Smarter interfaces that adapt to context.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Partnerships:</strong> Piloting YeahVibe in communities and workplaces.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 grid gap-6 items-start opacity-75" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); border-left:4px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(26,153,154,0.12); grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-display font-black text-teal-dark text-[1.2rem]" style="background:#E8F7F7;">3</div>
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block text-2xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-2 py-1 rounded-full mb-2" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05); color:#5A7A7A;">Future Vision</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink text-[1.15rem] mb-2">Phase 3: Integration — The Ecosystem</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-3">Scaling impact to influence societal well-being.</p>
            <ul class="ml-4 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1">
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">AI-Powered Guidance:</strong> Personalised decision support at scale.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Policy & Governance:</strong> Trusted resource for citizens and policymakers.</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Global Network:</strong> Architects and Instruments working worldwide.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-16 px-5" style="background:#F4FAFA;">
    <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="section-label justify-center flex">🧩 Philosophy</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-8" style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);">Every Step is Guided by Three Principles</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);">
        {[
          { icon:'🔓', title:'Accessible', desc:'Always free, modular, and easy to navigate.' },
          { icon:'🎯', title:'Practical',  desc:'Rooted in reality, not just theory.' },
          { icon:'🌐', title:'Universal',  desc:'Designed for everyone — from individuals to institutions.' },
        ].map(p => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6 text-center" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18);">
            <div class="text-[1.7rem] mb-2">{p.icon}</div>
            <h4 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-1">{p.title}</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted">{p.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Get involved -->
  <section class="py-16 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto">
      <div class="section-label">🤝 Get Involved</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-3" style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);">Help Shape the Future</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">This roadmap is built on collaboration. We need your voice to refine the instrument.</p>
      <div class="grid gap-5" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(26,153,154,0.12);">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style="background:#2ABFBF;"></div>
          <div class="text-2xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-teal-dark mb-2">Validate</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-2">Test & Give Feedback</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Test our tools and share your experience. <a href="https://form.jotform.com/222551513307043" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-dark font-semibold">Take our 1-Minute Survey →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden" style="background:white; border:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(26,153,154,0.12);">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style="background:#4CAF50;"></div>
          <div class="text-2xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-green-dark mb-2">Collaborate</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-2">Partner With Us</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Have a vision for a new feature? <a href="/contact" class="text-green-dark font-semibold">Contact us →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .grid[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .grid[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"]  { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .grid[style*="grid-template-columns:48px 1fr"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
